    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People tasked with gauging measures and weights, an exciseman who inspects dutiable bulk goods. The function was established in the Middle Ages and existed until the beginning of the 19th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
